data.description: DON'T LOSE OUT!!!  Great location, curb appeal and space, are all inclusive with this Charming rancher!! Located in the Central Sub, this 2 bed 1 bath 1 car detached garage may be just what you're looking for. Master bed has French Doors that open up to covered deck. Kitchen has ample cabinet space. Dining area can be used for dining OR a family room. Quiet neighborhood, yet just minutes from downtown Pueblo, where all the fun takes place. Privately fenced with space for a garden. Storage shed will stay and plenty of room for storage in the basement. Great back yard for entertaining, with the 14 X 12 covered deck. Priced to sell. Do you like being cozy?? Then check it out!!
